{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most probably in Russia, in Russian language, it has not got the same emphasis, not the same meaning as what it has in the English or in the Hungarian language.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't take any notice of me whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did, at that time, I don't know whether you're aware of it, the people who were fed by a-- the Jews in the ghetto, or in that protected house, we got something in our food which stops us from menstruating.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, automatically, when I was out of that ghetto already, for two or three weeks, and lived in that protected house, that was missing out of our-- and I started to get my period, which is not normal, one, but was a brownish.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, don't forget, I was full with life-- lice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had the same clothing on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, I mean the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From September on boots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was September, October, November, December, January.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was full, as I said, with this lice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my hair, and my body-- I had different lice in my hair and I had different lice in my body on the clothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know what water was like for shower or for washing yourself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was very unpleasant to know that three guys are there, raping you, when you have a period which is brown and, and ugly and--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, [SIGHS] after these-- well they weren't very satisfied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't cooperate with them, and they left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said you can take what you want, just showed me that I can take what I want from the flat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the time I got myself together, I got a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were no women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the men's apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no, no woman's clothing, but only men.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
